# 📜 Changelog  
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.  

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),  
and this project adheres to **Semantic Versioning**.  

---

## [1.2.0] - 2025-08-23  
### Added  
- 🚀 Finalized implementation of **Desi Drama GPT**  
- 📂 Completed corpus saving & download functionality  
- 🌐 Full language support for Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Punjabi, Marathi, Kannada, Gujarati, and Bengali  
- 🎨 Final UI polish with gradient background, styled buttons, and centered layout  

### Changed  
- Optimized model loading and generation for production use  
- Improved dialogue formatting for cleaner skit outputs  

### Fixed  
- Removed stray `contributing.md` bug in code  
- Handled empty skit generation gracefully  

---

## [1.1.0] - 2025-08-22  
### Added  
- Sidebar **Download button** to get saved skits as `.jsonl`  
- Asynchronous saving of skits (non-blocking UI)  
- Memory optimization with `torch.cuda.empty_cache`  

### Changed  
- Improved UI with custom CSS  
- Optimized model with 8-bit quantization and Flash Attention 2  

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-08-20  
### Added  
- 🎭 Initial release of **Desi Drama GPT**  
- Input fields for **Character 1**, **Character 2**, **Topic**, and **Language**  
- Generate button to create short, funny skits  
- Save generated skits into `corpus/desi_skit.jsonl`  

